Photo: Instagram Photo: Instagram Image 39 of 39 Selena Gomez proves to us all that being the seventh wheel at a Super Bowl party is no problem 1 / 39 Back to Gallery Like millions across the nation, singer and actress Selena Gomez gathered with friends to watch the Super Bowl Sunday night, but the Texas native pointed out one detail of the crowd she was with.
Everyone was coupled up in the group but her.
The 24-year-old shared a photo of everyone she hung out with on her Instagram story from Sunday night. The photo shows her sitting on the floor in front of three couples on a couch behind her. Each duo was cuddled up with one another and Selena drew corresponding hearts over each pair.
CELEB SUPER BOWL: These are the celebs that were in Houston for the Super Bowl
Selena, on the other hand, sat in front of them all with a beautifully fierce stare into the camera. Her eyes tell us that she is totally fine with being the 7th wheel at this Super Bowl party.
But her singleness begs the question, where is The Weeknd - her most recent reported love connection?After looking into The Weeknd's social media profiles, he didn't appear to do anything special for the Super Bowl.
But regardless, Selena proves to all of us that parties don't require a plus one to have fun. All we have to say is keep doing you, Selena - single or otherwise.
CONTROVERSY: Selena Gomez's newest photo has her in just a thong and her fans are not happy about it
